"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931969-Carlos-Alcaraz-Novak-Djokovic-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Carlos Alcarazmade a heartbreaking confession as he explained why he was in floods of tears after losing the Olympics gold medal match to Novak Djokovic.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 140, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old went 0/8 on break points and ultimatelylost in two close sets 7-6(3) 7-6(2).Immediately after the match, hestarted crying and had to stop a TV interview so he could gather himself.\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the match, Alcaraz addressed his emotional reaction and shared his disappointment.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7833537773645984e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought that I let all the Spanish people down a little bit, in some way,\\\" the world No.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Spanish people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"3 admitted.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that most of the Spanish people were waiting for my gold medal.\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Spanish people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And myself as well, I worked for it, I went for it [and] it could not happen so that's why I got emotional at the end because I could not make all the Spanish people proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Spanish people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But less than two hours after his defeat, Alcaraz was already feeling better.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7833537773645984e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"But thinking about that moment, it was really close at the end of the match.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not think [about] the things clearly and that's why I got emotional at the end.\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am right now thinking, I am going to say more relaxed.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I made them proud, I made them believe in a certain way.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am proud about the way I represented my flag.\\\"\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\":